
Getting started on Debain systems:

	# install requirements:
	sudo apt-get install build-essential dh-make pbuilder fakeroot debhelper devscripts gnupg python-pexpect

	# create gpg key:
	gpg --gen-key

	# setup pbuilder:
	cd ~
	echo "COMPONENTS=\"main restricted universe multiverse\"" >> ~/.pbuilderrc
	sudo pbuilder create

Getting started on Fedora systems:

	# add your user to the sudo group
	echo 'username ALL=(ALL) ALL' >> /etc/sudoers

	# install requirements:
	sudo yum groupinstall "Development Tools"
	sudo yum install rpmdevtools pexpect


